# Communication Prompts

Reference these prompts using: `@prompt-library/communication prompt-name`

## Clarifying Questions

**Use when:** Need to ensure understanding before proceeding

```
before proceeding ask me any clarifying questions of the following:
```

## Explain Only - Concise

**Use when:** Want explanation without code, keep it brief

```
your response is concise, no code
```

## Explain Only - Detailed

**Use when:** Want detailed explanation without code

```
do not include code in your response only explain it.
```

## Confirmation Check

**Use when:** Want to confirm understanding before proceeding

```
does this make sense? do you have any other questions? if you do not then tell me that you do not have any questions and ill tell you what to do. dont respond in code, just explain it to me
```

## Conversation Outline

**Use when:** Need summary of conversation

```
review this conversation in a concise outline
```

## Update Documentation

**Use when:** Need to check if docs/rules need updating

```
do we need to update any documentation or cursor rules based on the changes in this conversation?
```

